::Killfest/Scyther/Incarcinator::

"It closely resembles the pit," Killfest replies to Shivah, spotting Crater crawling up a scorched hill, "Do you have any bots that could get over here and get the wounded back to base?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Scyther reaches EndBringer, sighing and grabbing a hold of the much bigger bot. He flies off with some trouble, carrying EndBringer toward base.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Incarcinator lands near Demise, lifting him off with a bit less trouble than Scyther had and flying toward the Blackfortress.
